libpurple REST plugin
_____________________

Compile (on Debian/(K)Ubuntu)
-----------------------------

$ sudo apt-get build-dep pidgin
$ cd ~ && mkdir -p debian && cd debian
$ apt-get source pidgin
$ cd pidgin-X.Y
$ debuild -b -uc -us
$ ln -s <PURPLE_REST_SRC>/purple-rent.c ~/debian/pidgin-X.Y/libpurple/plugins/
$ cd build/libpurple/plugins
$ make purple-rest.so

